title: College Football Playoff Preview + Chris Rose talks Browns
itunes:title: College Football Playoff Preview + Chris Rose talks Browns
description:
DJ and Bucky are back with a new episode. First, the guys preview the College Football Playoff games and start by focusing on the Oklahoma vs. LSU matchup in the Peach Bowl, while also highlighting the top players to watch for on each team (1:27). Next, the duo discusses what they're looking forward to and players within the Clemson vs. Ohio State matchup in the Fiesta Bowl (18:41). Then, the pair analyzes who has the edge in the San Francisco 49ers vs. Seattle Seahawks big game in Week 17 (29:28). After that, DJ recalls his conversation with NFL and MLB Network's Chris Rose from the MLB Winter Meetings, as Rose talks about the Browns' season and baseball (32:05).
